comments.text:
> Shouldn't this be applied to all the wasm-godot jobs? @bbouvier can help with that.

No, only the Cranelift ones. Just to make sure we're on the same page, the intent here is to move all the Cranelift benchmarks to tier 2, so that would be wasm-godot on Cranelift, and wasm-misc on Cranelift. So I think the patch needs a small update here.
